targets.expr:
sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

(avg(
  max_over_time(jmeter_response_time_sum{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])  
  - min_over_time(jmeter_response_time_sum{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName))
/(avg(
  max_over_time(jmeter_response_time_count{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])     
  - min_over_time(jmeter_response_time_count{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName))
